The following examples are taken from existing hi-resolution mockups for GNOME System Settings and Initial Setup
With a fixed number of items the list has rounded edges.
In its scrollable configuration, the list has hard corners.
This example includes a search bar which live filters the content of the list.
In some cases, the list can only include a static single row.
The list can contain a mixture of icons and widgets, including spinners, buttons and switches.
The items in the list maintain a grid layout.
